'''disasters''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

Sets whether disasters can occur on a new map.<br><br>
true = disasters occur occasionally<br>
false = no disasters occur<br><br>
See [[en/Manual/Disasters]] for more information.

<pre>
[difficulty]
disasters = false
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ true | false ]

'''Default:''' false


